data.description:
Exciting new listing, awaiting your personal touch! A homeowner's dream, nestled on a 5.94-acre parcel of land in the serene beauty of Chesterfield County. This custom-built home offers an open first-floor, with a stunning primary BR featuring a walkout door leading to a deck, 3-sided gas fireplace (shared with the primary BA,) dual vanity, jetted tub, invigorating shower, walk-in closet, & an additional cedar-lined closet.
The living spaces in this home are designed for entertainment. The formal dining room has wainscoting, chair rail, crown molding, & resplendent hardwood floors. The living room is versatile, serving as an office or a 4th BR. The kitchen features a gas range, cherry cabinets, & a breakfast nook. The family room is a cozy haven with a fireplace, built-in's, and crown molding.
Upstairs, you'll find 2 spacious BR's connected by a Jack & Jill BA. Both BR's offer walk-in attics. Recent updates include a new roof in September 2017.
Outdoor lovers will appreciate the partially covered deck that overlooks a foot stone patio, as well as the front porch. This home emanates warmth & charm, creating an ideal atmosphere for entertaining family & friends.
